claim.claim-text:
An organic light-emitting display (OLED) device (100) comprising:
a pixel area (110) defined by a plurality of pixels (111) on a flexible substrate (101);
a non-pixel area around the pixel area (110);
a gate driver (113) in the non-pixel area;
a structure (140) in the non-pixel area configured to surround the pixel area (110);
a first encapsulation layer (131) covering the plurality of pixels (111), the gate driver (113) and the structure (140); and
a particle cover layer (132) covering the pixel area (110) and suppressed from being excessively spread by the structure (140).
